Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest pack

pack

Purpose:
  Pack a bounded Agent-readable context around one Wiki Graph object.

Usage:
  spinedigest pack <archive.sdpub> <uri> [--budget <chars>] [--json|--jsonl] [--help|-h]

Examples:
  spinedigest pack book.sdpub wikigraph://entity/Q162593 --budget 5000
  spinedigest pack book.sdpub wikigraph://chunk/123
